title: The Emperor’s Sword
description: The Emperor’s Sword Manhwa Zhu Yunwen, who barely survived the Jingnan campaign, received the souls of two of the world’s strongest martial artists, the First Heavenly Demon of the Demonic Cult and Huineng, the Sixth Patriarch of the Shaolin Temple, in his body, and was reborn as Heavenly Destroyer. This is the story of the Heavenly Destroyer’s journey to become an absolute existence begins! 황제의 검, The Emperor’s Sword
